(95, 67, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; padding: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\">9月2日，亚洲新天王李荣浩&ldquo;有理想&rdquo;世界巡回演唱会悉尼站在悉尼国际会议中心火爆开演。演唱会获得了澳洲知名天然植物护肤品牌Lacues变色口红和京东全球购的联名冠名赞助。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/0c46802c0dcdc49ede1faca1665b75cc.png\\" alt=\\"图片4.png\\" width=\\"552\\" height=\\"392\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　巡演从北京出发，一路持续发烧，将顶级音乐的魅力散播在了上海、香港、多伦多、洛杉矶、新加坡等世界各大城市。今天，身在悉尼的</font>&ldquo;鲸鱼&rdquo;和深度音乐发烧友们终于得以一饱耳福，尽情沉浸在&ldquo;老大&rdquo;感性的声线和充满爆发力的诠释之中。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/2d475f0d395cbdd7c152cd277885eaff.png\\" alt=\\"图片5.png\\" width=\\"546\\" height=\\"364\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　演唱会现场火花四射。李荣浩携手全球顶尖乐手团队和炫酷时尚的灯光舞美为观众奉上了一场直击心灵的视听盛宴。撕裂的呐喊声，是人们对偶像、对音乐以及</font>&ldquo;生活中的诗意和理想&rdquo;最高的礼敬!</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/71bab859697f3935fd18a4b69896cd38.png\\" alt=\\"图片6.png\\" width=\\"547\\" height=\\"365\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　《模特》、《李白》《老街》《不搭》、《不说》、《两个人》</font>&hellip;&hellip;一首接一首的金曲让现场高潮迭起。在李荣浩的声音里，观众找到归宿和共鸣，情不自禁的跟着合唱。演唱过程中，李荣浩多次走向观众进行互动。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\">　　时间没有淹没理想，反而磨砺出了深度。世上本没有一鸣惊人，是对理想的坚持，十几年如一日的匠心，成就了独具一格、万人追捧的李荣浩。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/d8b5ba9a7118ecc0135393523cc67f82.png\\" alt=\\"图片7.png\\" width=\\"553\\" height=\\"276\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　演唱会最后，李荣浩特别致谢了此次演唱会的冠名赞助商</font>Lacues变色口红以及京东全球购。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　正如李荣浩悉尼演唱会的主题一样，作为一家天然植物护肤品牌，</font>Lacues也有着自己的坚持和理想。一直以来，Lacues坚持天然、纯净、健康的理念，深耕天然有机护肤品，希望借助澳洲尖端生物科技与植物萃取工艺唤醒肌肤的生命力，成全女性之美。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　据悉，</font>Lacues的创始人悉尼时装模特Jasmine就是一位对护肤极为挑剔的西方美女。为了给更多包括模特在内的爱美女性带来纯净、安全、有效的高档护肤品，2010年，Jasmine充满热情的投入到了天然植物护肤品的研发之中&hellip;&hellip;</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　</font>Lacues最新推出的有机变色口红，就是为了帮助女性绽放天然之美横空出世的创新产品。口红以澳洲特产的天然羊毛脂、澳洲蜂蜡为基底，萃取霍霍巴籽油、凯恩斯有机椰子油等7种植物精华，配方温和、纯净，安全无刺激。口红含有的多种保湿因子，可帮助滋润唇部、淡化唇部细纹，让唇部愈发水润娇嫩。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:9.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;word-break:break-all;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/71bab859697f3935fd18a4b69896cd38.png\\" alt=\\"图片6.png\\" width=\\"547\\" height=\\"365\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　</font>Lacues有机变色口红运用独家温控技术，实现了唇温变色。口红可根据每个人的唇部温度和PH值自动调整唇部颜色深浅和色泽度，演绎千人千变的唇色盛宴。据悉，世界上第一代变色口红是由迪奥等一线品牌推出，而Lacues推出的这款有机变色口红，是澳洲第一款有机变色口红。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" style=\\"margin: 9pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\"><font face=\\"微软雅黑\\">　　有理想的音乐，终将被听见。有理想的品牌，终将被认可。未来，相信</font>Lacues有机护肤的理念会被更多人认可，Lacues旗下有机变色口红等爆款产品也将在全球得到风靡</span><span style=\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\">！</span></p>'),
(96, 67, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\">Lacues</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\">品牌于</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\">8<font face=\\"宋体\\">月</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">3</font><font face=\\"宋体\\">日在澳大利亚鼎力</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">赞助</font>2017<font face=\\"宋体\\">年林忆莲造乐者世界巡回演唱会悉尼的演出。林忆莲作为世界华语乐坛的灵魂人物，被誉为</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">&quot;</font><font face=\\"宋体\\">香港史上最高艺术成就的女歌手之一</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">&rdquo;</font><font face=\\"宋体\\">，具有炉火纯青的唱功和细腻而铿锵的嗓音，多年来深受广大华语世界及亚太文化圈歌迷的热爱。</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/7465f9af9f54c42b717fd1d44027203f.png\\" alt=\\"图片1.png\\" width=\\"288\\" height=\\"381\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">澳洲</font>Lacues <font face=\\"宋体\\">旗下拥有数十款有机护肤品和多款畅销全球的美容仪器，在澳大利亚本土市场具有极高市场占有率，此次赞助林忆莲演唱会，</font></span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\">是情怀的支持更看中</span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;\\">林忆莲的艺术成就。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/3eb668388faa56e968ddb94d28ae1835.png\\" alt=\\"图片2.png\\" width=\\"487\\" height=\\"325\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">口红是美妆产品里市场份额最大的品类，多年来一直为欧美品牌占主导，产品缺乏创新，随着以天然、健康、安全为特点的澳洲护肤美妆产品越来越受欧美、东亚国家消费者的欢迎，以澳洲</font>Lacues <font face=\\"宋体\\">、</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">EAORON </font><font face=\\"宋体\\">等一线品牌纷纷加大研发力度，推出了多个深受消费者热爱的产品。此次</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">Lacues </font><font face=\\"宋体\\">推出的有机变色口红正是充分体现了澳洲特色的全球新一代口红，它以澳洲的</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">6</font><font face=\\"宋体\\">种有机植物成分为核心原料，以高科技萃取精华为配方，实现了唇温变色，会根据不同的人不同时候嘴唇温度呈现不同的颜色，让口红的颜色与心情一致，每人只需一支，即可变出千种颜色。此外，澳洲</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">Lacues </font><font face=\\"宋体\\">有机变色口红的成份有机安全，连孕妇都可以用。据体验者反馈，它的滋润度和饱满度比一般口红要好，能坚持</font><font face=\\"Calibri\\">8</font><font face=\\"宋体\\">个小时不掉色。</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/ef7a22fd623fe4858a685ecb27ce3499.png\\" alt=\\"图片3.png\\" width=\\"474\\" height=\\"474\\" /></p>'),
(98, 67, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">随着近年来</font>LACUES产品在中国的畅销，一些不法造假之徒也开始把目光瞄向了这一澳洲天然植物护肤品牌，大肆进行造假，令消费者防不胜防，澳洲</span><span style=\\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\\">Lacues瘦脸仪</span><span style=\\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">就因为太过火爆而遭遇造假</font>,官方网址被各种高仿，这些造假分子手段隐敝，防不胜防。过去，提及假货、盗版，我们第一时间可能会想到电商。而现在，随着&ldquo;造假户&rdquo;野心的进一步扩张，他们开始把肮脏的触角伸向了官网。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/baefdd289115b461334a9c1e30a35032.png\\" alt=\\"图片1.png\\" width=\\"528\\" height=\\"453\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"justify\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.8000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">社会经济的不断发展，让爱美人士对美容护肤产品有了更高的追求，</font>LACUES源自澳洲天然植物，因而不仅热销澳洲本土，也广受中国消费者欢迎。然而由于信息不对称等原因，其被&ldquo;山寨&rdquo;、&ldquo;模仿&rdquo;的现象也更严重。LACUES 瘦脸仪是一款在澳洲指导价约624元的美容产品。LACUES瘦脸仪紧致提拉效果好，同时还可促进肌肤胶原蛋白再生、使肌肤更富有弹性。产品在澳洲、中国留学生群体以及美妆达人圈都颇受欢迎。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/df18fd1702b360a654a97aeca42e000c.png\\" alt=\\"图片2.png\\" width=\\"324\\" height=\\"539\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.7500pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"楷体_gb2312\\">【正品查防伪查询结果】</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:楷体_gb2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><img src=\\"/d/file/news/brand_news/2017-12-22/9ea007110ad0f68a5e1d8cb98ba70138.png\\" alt=\\"图片3.png\\" width=\\"408\\" height=\\"497\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"center\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.7500pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"楷体_gb2312\\">【造假货防伪查询结果】</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:楷体_gb2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"justify\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.8000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">造假的不法之徒利用各种手段，如国庆促销，双</font>12大促等噱头欺骗消费者上当，现在这款高科技美容产品的&ldquo;山寨版&rdquo;在网上被以80元的价格大肆售卖，还被LACUES官方&ldquo;抓包&rdquo;现行。注重消费者利益的LACUES不得不做出反击。为了打击造假者的嚣张气焰，LACUES从防伪码入手，破解了验证假货的&ldquo;密码&rdquo;。正品防伪的查询结果显示验证码为真实，且网页提供方为正确的官方网站。而造假产品的查询结果并没有明确说明验证码是否真实，且网页提供方为高仿官网！</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"justify\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.8000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\">LACUES为了保护消旨者利益，增强了通过科技手段验明证身的方法，除了通过上述方法可以确认产品真伪以外，为了积极配合市场，防止消费者上当受骗，LACUES还升级了新一代授权。在新授权中，LACUES利用多重随机码，水印匹配等科技手段对防伪验证进行了进一步加固。目前，LACUES的产品均通过官方公众号平台进行授权查询。只有随机码与店铺授权序号完全匹配才能进行查询。这就相当于为正版产品加了多重安全锁。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"justify\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.8000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">被称为</font>&ldquo;美丽经济</span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">的美容护肤产品市场是一个巨大的蓝海，作为澳洲一线护肤品牌，</font>LACUES对开拓中国市场非常重视，推出了多款新品满足消费者需求，但同时，这些产品也让造假分子们看到了&ldquo;商机&rdquo;，对造假、山寨的行为，LACUES作为品牌商也是深感鄙视。</span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">我们</font></span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">拿起有力武器捍卫品牌，将造假者绳之以法前，</font>LACUES</span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">始终</font></span><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">将消费者利益放在首位，以高科技为消费者营造出良好的购物环境。</font></span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p\\" align=\\"justify\\" style=\\"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:18.8000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:21.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:18.0000pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\"><font face=\\"宋体\\">未来，</font>LACUES在为消费者带来更多优质天然美容护肤产品的同时，也将利用科技手段不断加强防伪措施，同时配合相关部门对造假行为进行严厉打击，让造假行为无处遁形。</span><span style=\\"mso-spacerun:\\''yes\\'';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\\''Times New Roman\\'';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>'),
